  <module id="mod-1" title="Getting Started" order="1">
    <lesson id="les-1" title="Variables and Data Types" order="1" duration="PT40M">
      <content format="markdown">
        ## What are Variables?
        Variables store data values.

        ### Types
        - string
        - number
        - boolean
        - object
        - undefined

        **Task:** Create five variables using `let` or `const`.
      </content>

      <activity id="act-1" type="coding" est="PT20M">
